data.description: LOCATION!!  Centerville Bench!  only 3 short blocks above this home and the ATV & hiking trails begin.  Chef's kitchen features a duel door oven with a 5 burner GAS range,  3 level dishwasher, 3 drawer refrigerator w ice/water in  door, INDUSTRIAL GRADE range hood that can be removed & cleaned in the dishwasher & industrial grade garbage disposal....Primary Bedroom has its Own Full bathroom.  Another Full Bath near the side entry and Main Floor Laundry...  Main Floor Living if that is what you are looking for.  Lower level boost a Large Gathering Room, 3/4 bath and a Large bedroom and MORE THAN AMPLE storage, area for a Craft Room, Home Office or.... ?  1 Car Garage has plumbing and electrical.  Could possibly be 2 separate Units if you have the imagination.    *COPPER plumbing. *Water Heater 2020.    *Furnace serviced in October 2023 was was told it was in GREAT shape. *Smart thermostat & ALL cameras STAY for extra security, and which can  be controlled from your phone.  Seller says, "Best Neighbors Ever"
